Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  您叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  把那个打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我夫人穿过的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在尺寸应该很合身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  没什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作啊  还没有上轨道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和对策室的纪之关系好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  我有话跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于和饭纲家结亲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们双方都没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不考虑当事人的心意继续此事似乎不太妥当
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再听听你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  您收养了举目无亲的我并把我抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解此次结亲的目的重在加深亲戚间牵绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无反对的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣然接受此次婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「执　念」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快变强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐又多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是最近出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该让它熟悉工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾灵兽还真麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的灵兽只负责报告情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说麻烦  神乐你更甚几倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  还远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别考虑得太复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…什么  怎么了黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…也没…有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  永远是长不大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布向你问好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布也向你问好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新的灵力分布图啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  昨天确实记得这片地方有些异样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龟户的静止锋的话在今天早上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁把灵除掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我们之外还有很多自由退魔师存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市谷的同行者也壮大了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵行动起来也束手束脚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  你现代语考试得了几分？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐的事我可是了如指掌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看试卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道的话不看也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪理连篇的  是这张嘴说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉你擦什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没擦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布闻到香味了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布也闻到香味了噗露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是骗不了纳布先生的鼻子的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…刚刚买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛…比平时长了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛  我也会化妆的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  今天要和小纪约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  没这种安排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  感觉什么好难闻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  化妆品的怪味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是神乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是工作的地方  别把这种东西带过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的血统在鼻子方面可是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  你不知道怎么擦香水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得过量就像小孩子胡闹似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会适得其反喽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾香淡留就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用太多的话就跟浓妆大妈的味道一样了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心撒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少骗人了  你跟我有仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事就会向人泼咖啡的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  这是你身上的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己在那边散布气味  就别推在神乐身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你化浓妆没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大了又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  别在事务所里把灵兽召出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都把小乱和小不点收起来收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神宫寺室长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们两个到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简而言之就是性格不合啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场婚事可以继续谈下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪定大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无异议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入赘到统领一族的谏山家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实乃求之不得的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想尽快完成仪式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等黄泉从学校毕业再举行婚礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底是家世和权势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想能衷心为他们祝福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了啊  幽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  兄长大人也依然健朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说与饭纲家的那桩亲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要招婿入赘而让黄泉继承家主之位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉的确还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却拥有一副不辱谏山家之名的好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是黄泉可是养女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今还翻这陈年老账做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不想让她继承家业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初也不会把狮子王托付给她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样兄长大人难道要把家主之位传给没有谏山血统的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽  难道说抛弃了谏山家使命拒绝战斗的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今却想继承家主之位了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝非如此  兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想不通为什么偏偏把家业传给一个没血统的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个抛弃使命的人的确为谏山家蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有个女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女儿冥也拥有不辱谏山家之名的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您务必三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说错了  父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉小姐即使在退魔师中也算得上数一数二的剑术高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还负责照顾着丧母的土宫家小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在亲戚中也是备受信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂是我这等人能相提并论的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  奈落叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚约者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母定下的结婚对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够浪漫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是少女漫画情节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人郎才女貌  就像是流行电视剧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是月九吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（月九：每周一晚上九点播放的电视连续剧，是黄金档）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近发展得不太顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正烦恼要怎么样才能让他们好好相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…这样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  现在开始说明作战方针
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家无异议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先由变装成无赖的小一去袭击黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好路过的小纪解决了小一救出黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉立刻倾心于充满男子汉气概的小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人以Happy  End结束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我攻击…谏山？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…会丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那改变计划
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布先生代替小一去袭击黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把钱交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布No  No
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布也No  No
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那么岩端先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  男女的事外人还是不要插手为好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且万一他们分手了…饭纲说不定会喜欢上我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来在打这个算盘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  在商量什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  兄长到底中什么邪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用如此生气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们退魔师本来生命就不会长久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我继承了家主之位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一在执行任务中不幸丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主最后还是会落在黄泉小姐手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡说什么  冥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来考虑  万一黄泉小姐去世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许就能继承了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人再这么冷战下去  或许会影响到任务的执行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法  一次解决两个人是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先让黄泉对小纪回心转意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有喽  我的杀手锏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布就位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳布也就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认第一目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二阶堂桐  行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是二阶堂女士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭…饭纲君…今天负责巡逻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘谨  太拘谨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二阶堂小姐  再自然点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少见啊  二阶堂女士居然会穿裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有些私事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也穿这身到对策室来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会使工作场所增色不少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纪还真是个花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之第一阶段进行得还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就是让谏山看到这一幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉一定会魂不守舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体注意  第二目标接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近猛增起来真是麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与第二目标接触
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而毫无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐  Phase1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase1  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认命中目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然毫无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你演得不够大胆  再攻击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击进入  Phase2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二目标  一如既往地沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  心里肯定动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击进入Phase3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…二阶堂女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:16:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之  我们就别玩地下情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？不…你在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二目标离开战场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击无效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍  攻击无效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  刚刚的到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…那个原因有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标发生变化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不是适得其反吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉怎么看都更加生气了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能解释下这是怎么一回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有未婚妻了还在勾三搭四
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋？那是什么？你误会什么了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误会？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是遵从父亲定下的婚约而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我自信过头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能违背老爹只能乖乖听话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女人动手简直是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手这么重  没这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  说不定我们一直都会是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…性情不怎么相投
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉  小纪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起之后也会时常大打出手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架是不会间断的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能忍受这种生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还能回头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒绝就趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪之  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  全是我不好  都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄泉就像是我的姐姐一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚之后小纪就会变成亲哥哥一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人增加了  和和气气的不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我们会和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐  我不会惹你哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真万确吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据？要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就亲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看到你们的和好之吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样做神乐会满意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋  兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪…纪之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是此次作战成果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们又重新开始吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够呛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是神乐式的担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一身很美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新对我有兴趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真难得啊  竟然把它派到我家来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是自由行动的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  从来没到过我这哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它藏得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没道理察觉不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是说不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了防止看到我的秘密而使幻想破灭？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我想通过自己的双眼来观察你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能一直这么吵下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的  一直…持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是时间的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对谁来说都是同等的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:26.51,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:37.19,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:47.91,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.90,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:23:00.50,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.90,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:11.17,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:26.66,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:26.51,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾经对自己的心灵　许下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:37.19,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救赎　卷入叹息漩涡中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:47.91,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交错的时光转瞬即逝　道理的齿轮锈迹斑斓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.90,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已经无法后退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:23:00.50,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毁一切　亦无容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.90,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}为了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:11.17,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将那时仅有的幸福　深情拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:26.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}将远去的梦的足音　刻骨铭心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话  喰灵  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「美丽的敌人」


